text: Full time, after going 3-1 the game finishes 4-4. Still unbeaten though!
Match day- We face Central College Nottingham today at home, 1:30 kick off. Come on lads!
Full time! We walk away with another victory and a place in the second round! 1-0, played boys!
GOAL! Moffat scored another header from a corner. 1-0!
Line-up: 1-Ridley, 2-Booth, 5-Palethorpe, 6-Moffat, 3-Carvlin, 7-Humphrey, 4-Ludlow, 8-Evans, 11-Brewster, 9-Bradley, 10-Simon
GAME DAY- We travel to Bilborough College today for a first round cup match. Kick off 2PM
GOAL: Derby grab one back with a fierce drive that leaves Ridley with no chance. 2-1
RED CARD! The Derby player held on to Clarke's legs so he pushed him off and got dismissed, down to 10. Still 2-0.
GOAL! Bradley puts it in the bottom corner from the edge of the box. 2-0!
GOAL! Moffat with a glancing header at the near post from a corner. 1-0!
Today's XI: 1-Ridley, 2-Booth, 5-Moffat, 6-Palethorpe, 3-Carvlin, 7-Simon, 8-Evans, 4-Ludlow, 11-Humphrey, 10-Clarke, 9-Bradley.

FULL TIME! 4-1 victory against Bilborough College! Played boys
GOAL! Jack Clarke hits a left footed shot in to the bottom corner, 4-1!
GOAL! Dom Simon slotted the penalty to the keeper's right! 3-1
GOAL! Dom Simon laid it off for Corey Griffiths who slotted it over the keeper, 2-1
Goal, Bilborough equalised through a cross that swerved into the far top corner. 1-1
GOAL! Back pass from the goalkeeper bounces over his foot and Jordan Humphrey slots it in an open goal from 8 yards, 1-0!
